Package: ACESO
Title: A Cancer Evolution Simulation Optimizer
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Itziar", "Irurzun-Arana", email = "itzirurzun@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: ACESO is a multiscale computational framework to explore
    the evolutionary dynamics of heterogeneous tumor cell populations taking
    pharmacokinetic and drug interaction effects into account to rationally identify
    optimum single-agent and combination treatment administration strategies for
    oncogene-driven cancers.
Maintainer: Itziar Irurzun-Arana <itzirurzun@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4.3)
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
